        "description": "Smaller spots (50-200 μm) for fine detail cleaning on Gorilla Glass surfaces; larger (200-500 μm) for broad areas. 200 μm recommended for uniform coverage without pinpoint damage. Source: Equipment specifications from Trumpf and Coherent laser systems for precision optics cleaning."
